HEADWORD: Fountainless
<hw>Foun"tain*less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no fountain;
destitute of springs or sources of water.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Barren desert, <qex>fountainless</qex> and dry.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fountful</ent>⟦br⟧
